data.description: This residence boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms, complemented by a two-car garage. Tiled throughout the entire home, including the bedrooms. The property features an expansive floor plan, with a generously sized kitchen and family room—ideal for hosting gatherings and entertaining guests.  A/C units are approximately 2-3 years old, and you'll find a screened patio area, great for holding bbqs with family and friends. No Association.
